# Models Directory

This directory contains trained machine learning models for fake news detection.

## Files Structure

- `best_fake_news_model.pkl` - Main trained model
- `feature_extractor.pkl` - Text feature extraction model
- `vectorizer.pkl` - TF-IDF vectorizer
- `scaler.pkl` - Feature scaling model

## Model Performance

Current model performance metrics:
- Accuracy: ~85-90%
- Precision: 0.88 (Fake News)
- Recall: 0.82 (Fake News)
- F1-Score: 0.85

## Usage

Models are loaded automatically by the Flask API and can be used for:
1. Real-time news article classification
2. Batch processing of multiple articles
3. Feature extraction for analysis